Introducing our software, the Teaching-Learning Attainment System with CO-PO Mapping and Automation. This innovative solution emerges as a response to the evolving educational landscape in our college and also for others, where the effective assessment of teaching-learning outcomes is imperative for institutional success.
Designed to streamline the assessment process in educational institutions, our software is meticulously crafted to address the challenges faced by educators in measuring Course Outcome to Program Outcome (CO-PO) mapping attainment. By automating manual tasks and leveraging advanced algorithms, the software empowers educators to enhance teaching effectiveness while reducing administrative burdens.
